    <item>
      <title>英国就业改革将使企业每年损失高达 45 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/uk-employment-reforms-to-cost-firms-up-to-4-5-billion-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据对该政策的经济分析，英国工党政府的一揽子工人权利改革计划可能使企业每年损失高达 45 亿英镑（59 亿美元），小企业受到的影响尤为严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/uk-employment-reforms-to-cost-firms-up-to-4-5-billion-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:34:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院驳回上诉，特朗普阻止迈克尔·科恩提起诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/trump-averts-michael-cohen-suit-as-supreme-court-rejects-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院拒绝让唐纳德·特朗普接受其前律师兼调解人迈克尔·科恩的诉讼。科恩称，他之所以再次入狱，是因为他不愿承诺不公开批评他的前任老板。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/trump-averts-michael-cohen-suit-as-supreme-court-rejects-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普到访后，麦当劳告知员工其不支持政治候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/mcdonald-s-mcd-tells-workers-it-doesn-t-endorse-candidates-after-trump-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普周日访问宾夕法尼亚州一家餐厅后，麦当劳公司表示，它不会在总统选举中偏袒任何一方。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/mcdonald-s-mcd-tells-workers-it-doesn-t-endorse-candidates-after-trump-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:31:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国政府问责署称，全球最昂贵的武器计划六年来未能达到战备水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/f-35s-have-failed-to-hit-readiness-marks-for-six-years-gao-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国国会监督机构称，作为全球最昂贵的武器项目，F-35 的所有型号已连续六年未能达到最低战备率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/f-35s-have-failed-to-hit-readiness-marks-for-six-years-gao-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:12:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列逮捕七名涉嫌为伊朗从事间谍活动的公民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/israel-arrests-seven-citizens-suspected-of-spying-for-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列警方和安全官员称，七名以色列人因涉嫌为伊朗从事间谍活动以换取数十万美元而被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/israel-arrests-seven-citizens-suspected-of-spying-for-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:07:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举以来印度克什米尔地区农民工遭受大规模袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/india-s-kashmir-sees-major-attack-on-migrant-workers-since-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据警方称，周日，枪手在查谟和克什米尔地区一个重要的隧道项目中杀害了至少七名工人，另有五人受伤，这是印度动荡地区发生的基础设施项目遭受的最严重的袭击之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/india-s-kashmir-sees-major-attack-on-migrant-workers-since-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利计划将首都 Airbnb 式租赁税提高四倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/hungary-aims-to-quadruple-tax-on-airbnb-style-rentals-in-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班 (Viktor Orban) 领导的政府正采取措施解决布达佩斯日益严重的住房危机，匈牙利计划将短期租赁税提高近四倍，并暂停发放 Airbnb Inc. 式公寓的新执照。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/hungary-aims-to-quadruple-tax-on-airbnb-style-rentals-in-capital</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 12:35:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中印在习近平与莫迪可能举行会晤前结束边界僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/china-india-reach-border-pact-before-xi-modi-head-to-brics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度表示，它结束了与中国长达四年的边界僵局，这是缓解紧张局势的重要一步，为这两个核国家领导人本周在金砖国家峰会上举行会晤铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/china-india-reach-border-pact-before-xi-modi-head-to-brics</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:46:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国敦促黎巴嫩和加沙冲突在选举前停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/israel-hits-hezbollah-finances-as-us-eyes-diplomacy-in-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员前往中东，做最后的努力，以确保以色列与伊朗支持的真主党和哈马斯在下月初总统大选之前停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/israel-hits-hezbollah-finances-as-us-eyes-diplomacy-in-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 08:45:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
